Name: Weird Voices
Description:
The hero is beset by strange voices, calling them back home, into temptation, or towards insanity. 

Pick a song with extremely weird/affected vocals.

Name: Final Boss Battle
Description:
It's the decisive physical clash and philosophical showdown between the Hero and their overwhelmingly powerful Antagonist. There can only be one survivor.

Choose accompaniment for this climactic do-or-die attack!
